          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6749924">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6749924/" class="title-link">重要的君士坦丁堡</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6749924"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/59881801/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u59881801-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59881801/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">斑点紫罗兰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-07-21"
      class="main-meta">2014-07-21 15:06:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6749924_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在历史长河中，许多军事要地是必争的。有很多经典战役至今还是被人提起，有些已经进入了教科书。君士坦丁堡，提起这个名字，会想让人想起那百年前的重要战役。这场战役标志了罗马时代结束。  作者罗杰•克劳利，英国历史学家。因为对土耳其的历史感兴趣，多年行走于地中海，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6749924/#comments">(22回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">36有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
